cu.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to an invalid hexadecimal value 'invalid_id' will cause ID parsing errors during gNB initialization.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to an invalid hexadecimal value 'invalid_id' will cause ID parsing errors during gNB initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_ID 設定為無效的十六進位值 'invalid_id' 會在 gNB 初始化期間導致 ID 解析錯誤。
